# PLAYER::SET_PLAYER_MAY_ONLY_ENTER_THIS_VEHICLE

## Summary
Set the player can only entr this vehicle, set to null if you want them to enter any vehicle

## Parameters
* **PLAYER_INDEX** player
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicleID
